  "keyFeatures": [
    "MongoDB-backed REST API built with Java 21 and Javalin 7",
    "Full CRUD for branches, products, categories, suppliers, supplies, customers, and workers",
    "Advanced aggregation queries: low-stock detection, defective supplies report, branch product filtering",
    "React + TypeScript frontend with Tailwind CSS, PrimeReact, and React Router",
    "Generic controller/service pattern eliminating boilerplate for every resource",
    "Environment-based MongoDB connection via dotenv-java",
    "CORS enabled by default for development and cross-origin frontends",
    "Bruno API request collection included for rapid endpoint testing"
  ],
